<div id="review_289291744" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/289291744" />
    <a title="Maresa Ledford" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5895636-maresa-ledford"><img alt="Maresa Ledford" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/289291744?book_show_action=true">Mar 05, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Maresa Ledford" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Maresa Ledford" href="/user/show/5895636-maresa-ledford">Maresa Ledford</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer289291744" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15175153147149026399">I really liked this book. It was original and I loved the banter between the two lead characters. However, you need extensive knowledge of the pop culture of the 80&apos;s to understand their clothing choices, etc. </span>
  <span id="freeText15175153147149026399" style="display:none">I really liked this book. It was original and I loved the banter between the two lead characters. However, you need extensive knowledge of the pop culture of the 80's to understand their clothing choices, etc. </span>
