<li class='cover' id='bookCover_17166774'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17166774-shattered-promises"><img alt="Shattered Promises (Shattered Promises, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1417706092l/17166774._SX98_.jpg" />
